sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Dev as 👤 Blueprint Push (Main)
    participant Atomic as 📦 Atomic Workflows
    participant Security as 🛡️ Security Scanners
    participant Reg as 🏗️ GitHub Registry
    participant Assembler as ⚙️ Assembler Workflows
    
    Dev->>Atomic: Trigger foundations build
    activate Atomic
    
    Atomic->>Security: SAST (Semgrep)
    Security-->>Atomic: Pass
    Atomic->>Atomic: Compile native binaries
    Atomic->>Security: SCA/SBOM (Trivy/Syft)
    Security-->>Atomic: Pass (Artifact Verified)
    Atomic->>Security: Sign manifest (Cosign)
    
    Atomic->>Reg: Push artifacts-glibc/ssl/zlib
    deactivate Atomic
    
    Note over Reg, Assembler: Atomic foundation artifacts verified
    
    Assembler->>Reg: Run assemble-base.yml
    activate Assembler
    Assembler->>Reg: Pull verified artifacts
    Reg-->>Assembler: Download .tar.gz + SBOMs
    
    Assembler->>Assembler: Construct Monolithic Base
    Assembler->>Security: Sign Final OCI Manifest
    Assembler->>Reg: Push base:latest
    deactivate Assembler
    
    Reg-->>Assembler: Trigger follow-up layers
